snippet.title: Uncle Chop's Rocket Shop - Official Gameplay Trailer | gamescom 2022
snippet.description: Both adorable and disgusting, this trailer for Uncle Chop's Rocket Shop mixes cutscene and gameplay footage to give you a hint of the extremely bizarre tone. Fix spaceships and perform surgery to help little animals get back on their feet and in the air.
